# Video Search and Summarization (Cursor)

## Canonical instructions

For project-wide agent discovery, read
[`copilot-instructions.md`](../../.github/copilot-instructions.md). Do not
duplicate policy from that file or from skills. Use short pointers only in
Cursor rules.

## Skills

When the task touches VSS deployment, diagnostics, builds, summarization, or
video search, discover and read the relevant `SKILL.md` under
[`.github/skills/`](../../.github/skills/). Prefer
[`skill-catalog.json`](../../.github/skills/skill-catalog.json) for routing, but
do not assume a fixed list of skill files.

## Cursor workflow

- Prefer the repo's real interfaces: `setup.sh`, `build.sh`, Docker Compose,
  and the Pipeline Manager API at `/manager/...`.
- Run commands in the real environment when possible and investigate failures
  before giving up.
- Commits and pull requests only when the user asks.
- Keep changes minimal and match existing conventions in the touched area.
